art in theOlympicsin France.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1838, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999347808584262, \"rank\": 0.00046408013733266994, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1850, \"end\": 1866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\", \"score\": 0.9999999998760813, \"rank\": 1.1578107155399957e-10, \"text\": \"beach volleyball\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\"}, {\"begin\": 1881, \"end\": 1893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999973509439841, \"rank\": 2.6490630122755236e-06, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}, {\"begin\": 1946, \"end\": 1952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9989239763181852, \"rank\": 0.000755920318682854, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a convicted rapist\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his fourth and final match, Van de Velde again was subjected to a steady stream of hoots and whistles each time he served the ball.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2089,